CLICK TO VIEW TOP SHOOTING CATEGORIES









Equip yourself with the right tools for the hunt or range. Cabela's carries shooting equipment to satisfy all disciplines and preferences, featuring craftsmanship and technology that ensure a quality investment -- find it all at Cabela's.




Equip yourself with the right tools for the hunt or range. Cabela's carries shooting equipment to satisfy all disciplines and preferences, featuring craftsmanship and technology that ensure a quality investment -- find it all at Cabela's.
Cabela's selection of firearms includes rifles, shotguns, pistols, muzzleloaders and black-powder revolvers. Cabela's carries top firearm brands such as SIG Sauer®, Smith & Wesson®, Glock, Ruger®, Benelli, Remington®, Beretta and Savage® Arms.
Pistols can be used for target practice, home defense and self-defense.
Revolvers offer old-fashioned appeal and have delivered reliable performance on the range, and also for self-defense and hunting, since the 1800s.
Rifles are available in a wide variety of calibers. Customize your rifle with optics and other essentials for your favorite shooting activity.
Muzzleloaders extend hunting season and level the playing field with their one-shot capability.
Shotguns are excellent for home defense; shooting sports such as sporting clays, trap and skeet; and hunting game birds such as waterfowl and turkey.
Whatever you're aiming at, Cabela's has an extensive assortment of firearms to suit your needs.






